---
title: Recherche
description: Recherche interne sur l'ensemble des publications du CCRCSM — avis, textes, actualités, pages institutionnelles.
lead: La recherche porte sur les titres, descriptions et rubriques. Elle tolère les diacritiques (arabes et français) et la casse.
permalink: /fr/recherche/
searchable: false
breadcrumbs:
  - { label: "Recherche" }
---

<form role="search" class="search-box" data-search-form aria-labelledby="search-title">
  <label class="visually-hidden" for="search-input">{{ i18n[locale].search.placeholder }}</label>
  <input class="field__control" type="search" id="search-input"
         name="q" data-search-input
         placeholder="{{ i18n[locale].search.placeholder }}"
         autocomplete="off" maxlength="120" spellcheck="true">
  <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary">{{ i18n[locale].actions.search }}</button>
</form>

<p class="page__meta">{{ i18n[locale].search.help }}</p>

<div class="search-filters" role="toolbar" aria-label="Filtres de recherche">
  <button type="button" data-search-filter="all" aria-pressed="true">{{ i18n[locale].search.filters.all }}</button>
  <button type="button" data-search-filter="avis" aria-pressed="false">{{ i18n[locale].search.filters.avis }}</button>
  <button type="button" data-search-filter="texte" aria-pressed="false">{{ i18n[locale].search.filters.text }}</button>
  <button type="button" data-search-filter="actualite" aria-pressed="false">{{ i18n[locale].search.filters.news }}</button>
  <button type="button" data-search-filter="communique" aria-pressed="false">{{ i18n[locale].search.filters.communique }}</button>
</div>

<p data-search-status aria-live="polite" role="status" class="page__meta"></p>

<ul data-search-results class="search-results" aria-label="Résultats de recherche"></ul>
